---
title: One-Pan Beef & Rajas Quesadillas with Salsa Fresca, Southwest Crema & Guacamole
description: As we’ve grown more sophisticated in this life, so have our quesadillas. This real-deal quesadilla is packed with a cilantro-laden jumble of green pepper, onion, and tomato, plus two kinds of gooey, melty cheese. On top, there’s guacamole, fresh salsa, and a drizzle of spiced crema. A good thing just got a whole lot better.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/63d947be428d828d570e7932-5368adb8.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/65ccfc46cc89468059ab0565.pdf
time required: 30 minutes
source: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipes/one-pan-beef-and-rajas-quesadillas-65ccfc46cc89468059ab0565
author: HelloFresh
course: main course
servings: 2
cuisine: Mexican
nutrition:
  calories: 1030 kcal
  fat: 71 g
  saturated fat: 28 g
